description.en: The BTC RSI Crossover Yield Set attempts to capitalize on trends by detecting the speed and change of price movements for BTC. BTCRSIAPY automatically triggers rebalances if the Relative Strength Index (RSI) crosses below support at 45 or above resistance at 55 to indicate the price momentum. If the BTC RSI falls below 45, the Set will rebalance from BTC into Compound USDC and automatically accrues interest on your cash when the market is bearish.
